{"tid":231190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（戰鬥民族）俄男殺空管員為妻兒報仇，回國擔任副部長！ ","createTime":"2017-05-06T00:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T06:51:00.000Z","uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d87efa613822decacb1215eb28a472e51b2bbb1","tid":231190,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T00:21:20.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯建築師卡洛耶夫（Vitaly Kaloyev）妻子及一對年幼兒女不幸遇上空難，他認定事發時的空中管制員尼爾森（Peter Nielsen）要為事件負責，終在空難後兩年，親自到瑞士將他手刃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卡洛耶夫坦言，「&hellip;&hellip;入獄後我住進中度設防監獄&hellip;&hellip;我首次去『放風』時，幾乎所有人都來向我表達敬意。&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n卡洛耶夫2007年獲釋，回到北奧塞提亞-阿蘭共和國後被奉為英雄，後來更出任建築部副部長。"},{"pid":"c9301b4ea6a43d7dd867906e73ed7eaf2e341e4c","tid":231190,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T00:21:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170410/large/1491811193_396d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170410%2Flarge%2F1491811193_396d.jpg&h=010d2f10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca5e357581df02c05c355e1efd29e8961f8a08ac","tid":231190,"uid":40481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T00:22:46.000Z","msg":"機師兒子報仇 &gt; 部長第二兒子再報仇 &gt; 機師孫報仇 ..."},{"pid":"5477f8920f262bbe2b58f4a7effaff20c8ff65b9","tid":231190,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機師兒子報仇 &gt; 部長第二兒子再報仇 &gt; 機師孫報仇 ...</blockquote><br />\nTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0bfeeb785ed1b2c7a179301120362b3d19f7a37","tid":231190,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:03:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>機師兒子報仇 &gt; 部長第二兒子再報仇 &gt; 機師孫報仇 ...</blockquote><br />\nTVB<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咩TVB<br />\n<br